    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>Whether due to a velstrac's manipulations or a planar jaunt gone horribly wrong, your bloodline was infused with a vein of shadow.</p>\n<p><strong>Spell List</strong> occult</p>\n<p><strong>Bloodline Skills</strong> Occultism, Stealth</p>\n<p><strong>Granted Spells</strong> cantrip: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.mAMEt4FFbdqoRnkN]{Chill Touch}</em>; 1st: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.k34hDOfIIMAxNL4a]{Grim Tendrils}</em>; 2nd: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.4GE2ZdODgIQtg51c]{Darkness}</em>; 3rd: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.sRfSBHWHdbIa0aGc]{Chilling Darkness}</em>; 4th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.tlcrVRqW1MSKJ5IC]{Phantasmal Killer}</em>; 5th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.tcwT97RWKxsJiefG]{Shadow Siphon}</em>; 6th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.c3XygMbzrZMgV1y3]{Collective Transposition}</em>; 7th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.73rToy0v5Ra9NvL6]{Duplicate Foe}</em>; 8th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.wfleiawxsfhpRRwf]{Disappearance}</em>; 9th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.qDjeG6dxT4aEEC6J]{Weird}</em></p>\n<p><strong>Bloodline Spells</strong> initial: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.6UafOE1ZUbHamsZJ]{Dim the Light}</em>; advanced: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.0chL1b4OFIZxpN3v]{Steal Shadow}</em>; greater: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.HMTloW1hvRFJ5Z2D]{Consuming Darkness}</em></p>\n<p><strong>Blood Magic</strong> Shadows grow deeper around you or one target, either granting a +1 status bonus to Stealth or imposing a -1 status penalty to Perception for 1 round.</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feat-effects.Item.Nv70aqcQgCBpDYp8]{Effect: Shadow Blood Magic (Perception)}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feat-effects.Item.OqH6IaeOwRWkGPrk]{Effect: Shadow Blood Magic (Stealth)}</p>"
